                                <h3 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-white">Should I choose Cloud or
                                    Self-Hosted?</h3>
                                <span class="ml-6 flex h-7 items-center">
                   <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"
                        class="h-6 w-6 text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"><path
