                                    Self-Hosted involves setting up the FireCMS framework in your environment and
                                    pointing it to your existing database. Migrating from Self-Hosted to Cloud generally
                                    requires ensuring your configuration is compatible with the Cloud environment
                                    (especially regarding custom code).</p>
                            </div>
                        </details>
